sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Programme Modules Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open programme modules page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Load student's classes with programmes
    DB-->>LW: Programmes for student
    loop For each programme
        LW->>DB: Load programme modules + translations
        DB-->>LW: Modules list
    end
    LW-->>UI: Render programmes and module cards

    User->>UI: Refresh page
    UI->>LW: New request
    LW->>DB: Re-fetch classes/programmes/modules
    DB-->>LW: Latest data
    LW-->>UI: Re-render page
